---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About — Fesal Fayed" description="Who Fesal Fayed is: ML engineer in Miami, FIU Data Science & AI, fine-tuner of open models, builder of agentic infrastructure.">
  <article class="about">
    <h1>About</h1>

    <p>
      I'm Fesal. I live in Miami and I build machine learning systems.
    </p>

    <p>
      My particular interest is identifying siloed data sources and integrating
      them with world models, models that predict how current or past
      behaviors will affect future states and outcomes, to solve niche
      personal problems.
    </p>

    <p>
      I studied Data Science &amp; Artificial Intelligence at Florida
      International University, transferring from Health Science, pre-med
      track, at the University of Miami — pre-med is where logging my own
      biometrics, training and nutrition started. I especially love learning
      new ways to optimize the system around the model — the data pipelines
      feeding it, the interfaces it acts through, and the guardrails that let
      it run unattended.
    </p>

    <p>
      As of right now I've fine-tuned open models for agentic tool use. I
      adopted and now build on the Hermes autonomous agent; my
      <a href="/blog/gpt-oss-20b-tool-finetune/">gpt-oss-20b tool-calling
      family</a> ships in four formats and has crossed 14k+ downloads on
      Hugging Face.
    </p>

    <p>
      I run a personal data pipeline (quantified self) that pulls my wearable's
      biometrics and phone data (GPS, screen-time, and productivity). I log my
      strength training, nutrition and mental health journal data into one
      schema, which is the substrate for the world model I'm building to
      predict my own behavior.
    </p>

    <p>
      I'm also co-founder of a company still in stealth. Vertical intelligence
      for high-margin local operators. More on that when it's ready.
    </p>

    <p>
      I write <a href="/blog/">build logs and dissections</a> of these systems.
      I document my mistakes and failed attempts to hopefully provide some
      value to the community that has provided me with everything.
    </p>

    <p>
      Talk to me: <a href="mailto:hi@fesalfayed.com">hi@fesalfayed.com</a> ·
      <a href="https://github.com/fesalfayed">GitHub</a> ·
      <a href="https://huggingface.co/fesalfayed">Hugging Face</a>
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about { max-width: var(--measure); margin: 0 auto; padding-top: 2.2222rem; }
  .about h1 { font-size: 2.2222rem; letter-spacing: var(--track-display); }
  .about p { margin: 1rem 0; color: var(--fg-soft); }
  .about a { text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px; text-decoration-color: var(--line); }
  .about a:hover { text-decoration-color: var(--accent); }
</style>
